  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1 31\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd  \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Queue for cooking gas to end by 31st - Litro chief",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "By the 31st, standing in the queue for cooking gas will end, said Peiris, the head of the Litro company.",
        "Litro Company has started the distribution yesterday while the situation of not being able to import gas. Peiris said that they will distribute 120,000 gas cylinders from the morning of the 12th.",
        "While the prices for 12.5 kg cylinders have been increased, he has requested the public not to buy cylinders in the fake market as it has been decided to purchase 33,000 metric tons of gas by the end of July and 100,000 metric tons by the end of October.",
        "We have already taken the initial steps, we have signed an agreement with the World Bank, we have brought the necessary reserves to meet the needs of the people, so people will not have to stand in queues in the future, Litro said."
      ],
